Package: Classprob
Title: Calculate Classification Model Performance Metrics with Confidence Intervals
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("XJ", "H", , "huxiaojiang2021@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Description: This package provides functions to calculate various performance metrics for classification models, including AUC, sensitivity, specificity, NPV, PPV, and accuracy. It also computes 95% confidence intervals for these metrics using bootstrap methods.
